{"tid":345251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好鬼鍾意睇大陸啲軍事評論，笑餐死。","createTime":"2017-08-03T01:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T01:38:44.000Z","uid":107324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"597bbad90f4a375ebfd3e87cbbe6bbbadc25731c","tid":345251,"uid":107324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"同一個人既文<br />\n<br />\n第一篇(06/07)<br />\n美空軍一直關注於隱身技術的發展，認為只有隱身可以解決一切難題，可以憑藉隱身優勢隨意欺負對手，卻忘了一點，<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;道高一尺，魔高一丈&rdquo;，當隱身技術興起，必然帶動反雷達技術的發展，中國在這方面相當積極，而且研發出全新的反隱身技術：DWL001系統。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.sohu.com/a/154794020_600487?_f=m-article_10_feeds_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F154794020_600487%3F_f%3Dm-article_10_feeds_1&d=SHH32FSuR7JfMzJBwEk31f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=de246c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.sohu.com/a/154794020_600487?_f=m-article_10_feeds_1</a><br />\n<br />\n第二篇(02/08)<br />\n那麼國產殲20戰機隱身性如何？其實，這個不需要太多的解說了，只要看一下照片，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中的一個細節足以證明，殲20的隱身性非常好，可以連自家雷達也一起騙過了，</span>這就是殲-20機身下偶爾會掛載了一個小裝置，以前美軍F-22戰機也曾多次被拍到掛載此裝置的照片，它學名為：龍勃透鏡，可以無限放大的雷達反射波，加掛它的目的就是讓普通雷達可以發現自已，以避免誤會等，<span style=\"color: red;\">既便殲20需要加掛它，說明其隱身性與F22相當。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.sohu.com/a/161773040_600487/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F161773040_600487%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=SHH32FSuR7JfMzJBwEk31f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8e99914f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.sohu.com/a/161773040_600487/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a><br />\n<br />\n最強之矛VS最強之盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.funtory.tw/2012/08/120809-Contradiction/Contradiction_cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.funtory.tw%2F2012%2F08%2F120809-Contradiction%2FContradiction_cover.jpg&h=f46b73dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f675aca949468202df1bdcf2a6a2e2df03abb850","tid":345251,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6dedfb47aedf22acc23032f66a33d9981b3443b9","tid":345251,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T01:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec639e49ea92f9d68e963f3303567ae39b9a9ca","tid":345251,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"007 達聞西？"}]}